  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd, \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd -\u00a0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb8 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "United People's Shakti is ready to bring political and economic stability in the country - Thissa Athanayake",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "To take up this challenge, it has been decided to propose the name of Opposition Leader Sajith Premadasa for the post of Interim President, MP Tissa Athanayaka said.",
        "He stated this at a press conference held on Tuesday 12th at the office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo, while he further mentioned,",
        "The country can be rebuilt. Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa is ready to accept that challenge.",
        "Similarly, leaders of other opposition parties are also ready for this. We are carrying out discussions with other parties in this regard.",
        "For this, all the parties in the Parliament should come together and come out of this crisis. No one can shirk this responsibility.",
        "The political agenda is not important in the current situation. No one cares about their party or cause. It is necessary to recover the country from the massive crisis it is currently facing.",
        "The United People's Power Party is expected to act responsibly to restore political stability and economic stability in the country.",
        "He said that United People's Power has unanimously decided to propose the name of Opposition Leader Sajith Premadasa for the post of Interim President."
      ],
